data.description: Corner Lot in sought after neighborhood. This one will not last long. 4 bedrooms, 3 baths, open concept living room kitchen and dinning.  Big front porch and back porch that overlooks the pool. The pool will need a liner. There is an office space or a space that could be used for a nursery next to the main bedroom. Nice storage in attic with permanent stairs. Close to schools, shopping and churches. Call me today. Security system does not convey
